Class DynamicRouter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.camel.support.ServiceSupport

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsyncProcessor, Processor, Service, ShutdownableService, HasId, IdAware, StatefulService, SuspendableService, Traceable

    public class DynamicRouter
extends RoutingSlip
    Implements a Dynamic Router pattern where the destination(s) is computed at runtime.

    This implementation builds on top of RoutingSlip which contains the most logic.
